'''Mbhazima Samuel (Sam) Shilowa''' (b [[April 30|30 April]] [[1958]]) ke tonakgolo ya [[Gauteng]], [[Afrika Borwa]].

Shilowa o belegwe Olifantshoek yeo lehono e elego [[Limpopo]]. O phetile dithuto tša gage Akani High School ka [[1978]]. Ngwageng o latelago aya [[Johannesburg]] go nyaka mošomo. O thomile go šoma John Weinberg Hardware [[Germiston]]. Go tloga mowe aya [[Anglo Alpha Cement]] [[Roodepoort|Rooderpoort]], morago aya PSG Services - Johannesburg. ka 1981, Shilowa e bile leloko la mokgatlo wa babereki. O kgethilwe goba motlatša moperesidente morago yaba moperesidente wa [[SATAWU|South African Transport and Allied Workers Union]].

Ka 1999 o kgethilwe goba tonakgolo ya [[Gauteng]].

